INSERT INTO
            message
            (
                channel_name,
                channel_id,
                author_name,
                author_discriminator,
                author_id,
                author_avatar_url,
                author_bot,
                guild_name,
                guild_id,
                guild_icon_url,
                message_content,
                message_id,
                message_clean_content,
                message_reference_channel_id,
                message_reference_guild_id,
                message_reference_message_id
            )
        VALUES
            (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
